2886	Configurable related items	ross		"Related items (Apps & Ideas) have a collection of types, which are currently fixed.  Some of these types are ambiguous, such as ideas in that they may not have a link - and if they do it is likely to be to a blog post - another existing type.

Whilst the URL is required, and we think this should stay required, we should also allow users to change the types found in Apps & Ideas to a shortened list that suits their requirements."	enhancement	new	awaiting triage	ckan 2.0	ckan				ckan	none
